, RESPECTIVELY.

THE COMPANY ALSO HAS A LONG-TERM INCENTIVE PLAN (“LTIP”) THAT WAS ADOPTED BY THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS AND APPROVED BY SHAREHOLDERS IN SEPTEMBER 1997 AND LATER AMENDED IN FISCAL 2007. THE COMPANY RECOGNIZED

$46 MILLION

,

